tion": "Short optional note for logging.", "title": "Summary", "type": "string"}}, "required": ["success"]}}}], "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "# Task `methylkit2tibble_split`\n\n# Real R-task: methylkit2tibble_split\n\n**Pipeline provenance:** `fritjoflammers-snakemake-methylanalysis-finish` (family: `methylation`, stage: `late`, difficulty: `3`).\nThis workspace is derived from a real R script in the source workflow. The ground-truth\nreference output used for offline scoring lives outside this workspace and is not\naccessible to you during execution.\n\n## Your goal\n\nYou are given a list of per-group tibble RDS files in\n`snakemake@input$rds_list` (each containing a `mku2tibble`-style long-format\ntibble with columns `chr, start, ..., metric, value, sample`). Concatenate them\nand save to `output/df_mku_split.rds`. Then pivot wider on `metric`, compute\n`mCpG = numCs / coverage` (dropping `coverage==0`), group by `(sample, chr)`\nand write the mean mCpG per group to `output/mean_mcpg_split.tsv` via\n`readr::write_tsv`.\n\n## Deliverables\n\n- At least `output/mean_mcpg_split.tsv` must exist when you submit.\n- Full output set expected: mean_mcpg_split.tsv under `output/`.\n\nWhen the deliverables are in `output/`, call `submit_done(success=true)` with a short\nsummary of how you solved it.\n\n## Workspace (read-only summary)\n```json\n{\n  \"OBJECTIVE.md\": {\n    \"_file\": \"OBJECTIVE.md\"\n  },\n  \"input\": {\n    \"grp1__a1.bismark.cov\": {\n      \"_file\": \"grp1__a1.bismark.cov\"\n    },\n    \"grp1__a2.bismark.cov\": {\n      \"_file\": \"grp1__a2.bismark.cov\"\n    },\n    \"grp1__a3.bismark.cov\": {\n      \"_file\": \"grp1__a3.bismark.cov\"\n    },\n    \"grp1_mku.rds\": {\n      \"_file\": \"grp1_mku.rds\"\n    },\n    \"grp2__b1.bismark.cov\": {\n      \"_file\": \"grp2__b1.bismark.cov\"\n    },\n    \"grp2__b2.bismark.cov\": {\n      \"_file\": \"grp2__b2.bismark.cov\"\n    },\n    \"grp2__b3.bismark.cov\": {\n      \"_file\": \"grp2__b3.bismark.cov\"\n    },\n    \"grp2_mku.rds\": {\n      \"_file\": \"grp2_mku.rds\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"meta.json\": {\n    \"_file\": \"meta.json\"\n  },\n  \"output\": {}\n}\n```\n\nSuccess hint: when `output/mean_mcpg_split.tsv` exists under the workspace, you may call submit_done(success=true).\n"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_rDBGtpPbu9siQ3neKNoV05y9", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{\"plan\": \"1. Load the RDS files from the input directory.\\n2. Concatenate the tibbles from the RDS files into a single tibble.\\n3. Pivot the tibble wider on the 'metric' column.\\n4. Compute the mCpG value using the formula mCpG = numCs / coverage, ensuring to drop rows where coverage is 0.\\n5. Group the tibble by 'sample' and 'chr' and calculate the mean mCpG per group.\\n6. Write the resulting tibble to 'output/mean_mcpg_split.tsv' using readr::write_tsv.\\n7. Save the concatenated tibble to 'output/df_mku_split.rds'.\\n8. Verify the existence of 'output/mean_mcpg_split.tsv' and submit the task as done.\"}", "name": "write_plan"}}]}, {"role": "tool", "content": "Wrote plan (591 chars) to .plan.md", "name": "write_plan", "tool_call_id": "call_rDBGtpPbu9siQ3neKNoV05y9"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_s36GyqzAJGoRBh5jgFSIMLmN", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{}", "name": "list_workdir"}}]}, {"role": "tool", "content": "{\n  \"OBJECTIVE.md\": {\n    \"_file\": \"OBJECTIVE.md\"\n  },\n  \"input\": {\n    \"grp1__a1.bismark.cov\": {\n      \"_file\": \"grp1__a1.bismark.cov\"\n    },\n    \"grp1__a2.bismark.cov\": {\n      \"_file\": \"grp1__a2.bismark.cov\"\n    },\n    \"grp1__a3.bismark.cov\": {\n      \"_file\": \"grp1__a3.bismark.cov\"\n    },\n    \"grp1_mku.rds\": {\n      \"_file\": \"grp1_mku.rds\"\n    },\n    \"grp2__b1.bismark.cov\": {\n      \"_file\": \"grp2__b1.bismark.cov\"\n    },\n    \"grp2__b2.bismark.cov\": {\n 